### ============================================================================
### SYSTEM — /api/v1/system-logs + /api/v1/system-settings + /api/v1/settings
### ============================================================================

### ─── System Logs — /api/v1/system-logs ─────────────────────

### List system logs (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system-logs?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get system log by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system-logs/{{systemLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create system log
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "level": "INFO",
  "message": "User completed onboarding",
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.1",
  "userAgent": "Mozilla/5.0"
}

### Update system log
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system-logs/{{systemLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "level": "WARN",
  "message": "Updated: User completed onboarding with warnings"
}

### Delete system log
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system-logs/{{systemLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ─── System Settings — /api/v1/system-settings ─────────────

### List system settings (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system-settings?page=0&size=20

### Get system setting by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system-settings/{{systemSettingId}}

### Create system setting
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system-settings
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "MAINTENANCE_MODE",
  "value": "false",
  "type": "BOOLEAN",
  "description": "Enable maintenance mode"
}

### Update system setting
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system-settings/{{systemSettingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "MAINTENANCE_MODE",
  "value": "true",
  "type": "BOOLEAN",
  "description": "Enable maintenance mode"
}

### Delete system setting
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system-settings/{{systemSettingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ─── User Settings — /api/v1/settings ──────────────────────

### Get my settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Accept questionnaire consent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/settings/questionnaire-consent
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
